Choice of welding technology for steels of different types using dynamic and cyclic fracture toughness criteria
column2: LI Maslov, EI Kolokolov, VV Roshchin - Svarochnoe Proizvodstvo, 1978 - inis.iaea.org
column12: [en] Carried out has been a comparative evaluation of dynamic and cyclic fracture toughness and critical lengths of cracks of welded joints of steel-20+ steel-Kh18N10T obtained with austenitic and low-carbon filler materials. The weldments have been tested …
